query:
select
    se.id,
    public_url as "public_url!",
    se."name" as "name!",
    status_code as "last_status!",
    sh."created" as "last_update!"
from status_entry as se
inner join
    (
        select status_id, status_code, created
        from status_history
        order by created desc
        limit 5
    ) as sh
    on sh.status_id = se.id
